---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
import PageHeader from "../components/PageHeader.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="About"
  description="About Luca Silveira: product manager and business student interested in AI, logistics, marketplaces, global markets, and Brazil."
>
  <PageHeader
    eyebrow="About"
    title="A practical curiosity for products, markets, and how work actually gets done."
    description="I am drawn to messy operating environments where the right product can make judgment, coordination, and trust easier."
  />

  <div class="prose-archive max-w-3xl">
    <p>
      I am Luca Silveira, a product manager and business student based in Miami, FL.
    </p>
    <p>
      My work has sat across logistics, marketplaces, growth, investing research, and
      consulting. At Uber Freight, I am focused on product problems around shipment
      context, AI-generated summaries, and risk reasons. Before that, I worked with
      Instawork, Fuse Capital, and Bond Consulting Group.
    </p>
    <p>
      I care about product work that respects operational detail. The more I learn, the
      more interested I become in the gap between elegant software and the real-world
      systems it has to live inside.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
